### Criar usuário 1
POST http://localhost:8081/api/usuarios
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nome": "Leonardo Silva",
  "email": "leo@email.com",
  "idade": 30
}

### Criar usuário 2
POST http://localhost:8081/api/usuarios
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nome": "Maria Santos",
  "email": "maria@email.com",
